Name: Mori The Piercer
level1 ability: Disintegrate a female operator with 2 defense or less
level2 ability: Move and Strike [3] if Mori already moved this turn
special ability: Once Mori uses the move action he may Strike [1]
flavortext: I live by a code. The code says nothing about time travel.

Name: Angela Storm
level1 ability: Strike [2] and move target to Ben Storm's turnpoint (if he is active)
level2 ability: Disable all male operators
flavortext: Ask me if this is the worst I can do. Please.

Name: Ben Storm
level1 ability: Strike [2] and move target to Angela Storm's turnpoint  (if she is active)
level2 ability: Ambush: Disable any operator that moves into his turnpoint on opponent's next turn
flavortext: You think my ambitions are twisted? You haven't met my twin sister.

Name: Ben Storm
level1 ability: Change a turnpoint to any type of agenda for 2 turns
level2 ability: Immobilize operator, anywhere on board
special ability: When activated, disable Ben and/or Angela Storm
flavortext: Join me outside the box, dead and alive.

Name: Akane
level1 ability: Give +2 armor to a friendly operator
level2 ability: Haven: Reactivate a disabled operator and give them +1 armor
special ability: If Akane is in the same turnpoint with Mori, she must move away by the end of the turn, even if she has already moved.
flavortext: Not like this' I asked, but he had two needs of me.

Name: The Pale Man
level1 ability: Strike [1] one century up or down-stream
level2 ability: Strike [3]
flavortext: I do not have higher functions.

Name: Mia Star
level1 ability: Give +1 armor to all Orbital Strike operators on the board
level2 ability: Strike [2] 3 times
special ability: When moving, can take along a friendly operator
flavortext: My mind is a star and my palms are solar sails.

Name: Augur, Stream-Phase Shaman
level1 ability: Channel: switch Augur with any disintegrated operator. Switch back if disabled. Augur returns disabled.
level2 ability: Stream-shade: create a double that mirrors Augur's actions in another stream, always in the same century. [see FAQ]
special ability: When Augur's ability effect should end, pay (1x) to prolong it for 1 turn
flavortext: The dead call to me from the void between the streams. I feed the living to them.

Name: Man Bon-Hwa
level1 ability: Strike [2] across stream
level2 ability: Disintegrate an operator activated on opponent's previous turn
special ability: Cannot be struck by female operators
flavortext: I adore women, the pinnacle of their free will is slavery. All they need is the right master.

Name: Big Boy
level1 ability: Strike [2]
level2 ability: Lockdown: no operator can move in or out of Big Boy's turnpoint
special ability: Can be activated in any turnpoint but cannot move on it's own
flavortext: Make room. Or don't.

Name: Little Boy
level1 ability: Move opponent's operator from any turnpoint to current
level2 ability: Move opponent's operator from current to any turnpoint
flavortext: Fasten your seatbelts.

Name: Sourayah The Bad Prophet
level1 ability: Select a turnpoint upstream. A random operator there gets -2 armor
level2 ability: Dark visions: choose a male operator anywhere on board. During opponent's next turn that operator is immobilized and must use Strike ability on anyone he can.
flavortext: They all think they need me, freely willing to sacrifice so much. This is how my gift works.

Name: Aran
level1 ability: Strike [3]
level2 ability: Strike [2] to an untouchable operator
special ability: Can move into a turnpoint that is affected by any movement preventing ability. Cannot be immobilized
flavortext: I am like the ham'sin: desert wind, dust, and pain.

Name: Layla
level1 ability: Reactivate a disabled operator from Unit 707
level2 ability: Reactivate a disabled operator. If operator belongs to opponent, pay (1x) and assume control for 2 turns
special ability: Can move 2 times in a turn
flavortext: If the desert sand does not do it first, I will drink all your body fluids.

Name: Hamdi
level1 ability: Give +3 armor to an operator from Unit 707
level2 ability: Strike [3]
flavortext: Blood sometimes gets mixed in my black coffee, I like the taste.

Name: Marwa
level1 ability: Recall: move all operators of unit 707 to her turnpoint
level2 ability: Disable all male operators in her turnpoint
special ability: All members of unit 707 can be activated on Marwa's turnpoint
flavortext: Some thought I was too pretty to give commands.

Name: Dr. Koh
level1 ability: Viral decay: all opponent operators in the stream get -1 armor
level2 ability: Bring back a disintegrated operator, put them in 2200
flavortext: You see yourself as a whole, in form and mind, but you are not. Let me show you.

Name: Captain Shortspear
level1 ability: Move. After moving becomes untouchable
level2 ability: Strike [2] at 2 targets
flavortext: You won't pick me out in a crowd, not until my pistol is in your face.

Name: Soren Glasskin
level1 ability: Use an ability that any other operator in the same stream may use [must pay its price]
level2 ability: Take control of an opponent's operator for 2 turns. Soren is disabled for 2 turns.
flavortext: You keep calling me Soren, you really shouldn't.

Name: The Gray Baron
level1 ability: Strike [2]
level2 ability: Spin agenda instantly without ripple effect
flavortext: Men of power cast dark shadows. The closer a woman gets, the easier for her to hide in them.

Name: Dr. Ro_u
level1 ability: Disintegrate an operator disabled on this turn
level2 ability: Give a friendly operator +3 armor
flavortext: They never suspect.

Name: Mr. Ro_u
level1 ability: Create a drone with Strike [1] (1m)/ 1 defense
level2 ability: EMP Strike: Disable all target opponent's operator drones and tech
special ability: Can build up to 3 drones. The drones are destroyed when Mr. Ro_u is disabled
flavortext: If the devil grants you your wish, is he still the devil? Or do you become the devil by paying his price?
